{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775849862296,"sessionID":"ses_28719b16dffecOLQtjnU5U7KHJ","part":{"id":"prt_d78e67482001rcW8bPTS2sm6Fl","messageID":"msg_d78e66c8f0010MykTRLi2nfW6C","sessionID":"ses_28719b16dffecOLQtjnU5U7KHJ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-6a5ff5819ef24bffaebd69485f80675c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n2: \n3: **Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`\n4: **Language:** Go\n5: **Size:** S\n6: \n7: ## 垃圾回收核心结构\n8: \n9: ### 场景: 定义 GarbageCollector 结构体\n10: \n11: **GIVEN** 需要定时清理空闲和过期的 Sandbox 资源\n12: **WHEN** 定义垃圾回收器核心结构体\n13: **THEN** 创建 `garbage_collector.go` 文件，定义 `GarbageCollector` 结构体\n14: \n15: ```go\n16: type GarbageCollector struct {\n17:     dynamicClient dynamic.Interface\n18:     storeClient   store.Store\n19:     interval      time.Duration\n20:     ctx           context.Context\n21:     cancel        context.CancelFunc\n22: }\n23: ```\n24: \n25: ### 场景: 定义 Sandbox 资源 GVR\n26: \n27: **GIVEN** 需要操作 Kubernetes 的 Sandbox 和 SandboxClaim 资源\n28: **WHEN** 定义资源 GroupVersionResource\n29: **THEN** 声明 Sandbox 和 SandboxClaim 的 GVR 常量\n30: \n31: ```go\n32: var (\n33:     SandboxGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n34:         Group:    \"agents.x-k8s.io\",\n35:         Version:  \"v1alpha1\",\n36:         Resource: \"sandboxes\",\n37:     }\n38: \n39:     SandboxClaimGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n40:         Group:    \"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\",\n41:         Version:  \"v1alpha1\",\n42:         Resource: \"sandboxclaims\",\n43:     }\n44: )\n45: ```\n46: \n47: ## 清理原因类型定义\n48: \n49: ### 场景: 定义 Sandbox 清理原因\n50: \n51: **GIVEN** 需要区分不同的 Sandbox 清理场景\n52: **WHEN** 定义清理原因枚举类型\n53: **THEN** 在 `types/sandbox_types.go` 中定义 `SandboxCleanupReason` 类型\n54: \n55: ```go\n56: type SandboxCleanupReason string\n57: \n58: const (\n59:     CleanupReasonManual      SandboxCleanupReason = \"manual\"\n60:     CleanupReasonIdleTimeout SandboxCleanupReason = \"idle_timeout\"\n61:     CleanupReasonExpired     SandboxCleanupReason = \"expired\"\n62: )\n63: ```\n64: \n65: ### 场景: 定义清理审计日志条目\n66: \n67: **GIVEN** 需要记录 Sandbox 清理操作的审计信息\n68: **WHEN** 定义审计日志条目结构\n69: **THEN** 在 `types/sandbox_types.go` 中定义 `CleanupAuditEntry` 结构\n70: \n71: ```go\n72: type CleanupAuditEntry struct {\n73:     SessionID    string               `json:\"sessionId\"`\n74:     SandboxID    string               `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n75:     Namespace    string               `json:\"namespace\"`\n76:     Reason       SandboxCleanupReason `json:\"reason\"`\n77:     DeletedAt    time.Time            `json:\"deletedAt\"`\n78:     Success      bool                 `json:\"success\"`\n79:     ErrorMessage string               `json:\"errorMessage,omitempty\"`\n80: }\n81: ```\n82: \n83: ## 垃圾回收器初始化\n84: \n85: ### 场景: 创建垃圾回收器实例\n86: \n87: **GIVEN** 已有 dynamic client 和 store client\n88: **WHEN** 创建垃圾回收器实例\n89: **THEN** 初始化所有字段并创建可取消的 context\n90: \n91: ```go\n92: func NewGarbageCollector(\n93:     dynamicClient dynamic.Interface,\n94:     storeClient store.Store,\n95:     interval time.Duration,\n96: ) *GarbageCollector {\n97:     ctx, cancel := context.WithCancel(context.Background())\n98:     return &GarbageCollector{\n99:         dynamicClient: dynamicClient,\n100:         storeClient:   storeClient,\n101:         interval:      interval,\n102:         ctx:           ctx,\n103:         cancel:        cancel,\n104:     }\n105: }\n106: ```\n107: \n108: ## 生命周期管理\n109: \n110: ### 场景: 启动垃圾回收器\n111: \n112: **GIVEN** 垃圾回收器实例已创建\n113: **WHEN** 调用 Start 方法\n114: **THEN** 启动独立的 goroutine 运行 GC 循环\n115: \n116: ```go\n117: func (gc *GarbageCollector) Start() {\n118:     go gc.gcLoop()\n119: }\n120: ```\n121: \n122: ### 场景: 停止垃圾回收器\n123: \n124: **GIVEN** 垃圾回收器正在运行\n125: **WHEN** 调用 Stop 方法\n126: **THEN** 取消 context，优雅停止 GC 循环\n127: \n128: ```go\n129: func (gc *GarbageCollector) Stop() {\n130:     gc.cancel()\n131: }\n132: ```\n133: \n134: ## GC 循环机制\n135: \n136: ### 场景: 实现 GC 循环\n137: \n138: **GIVEN** 垃圾回收器已启动\n139: **WHEN** GC 循环运行\n140: **THEN** 定时执行 tick 方法，直到 context 被取消\n141: \n142: ```go\n143: func (gc *GarbageCollector) gcLoop() {\n144:     ticker := time.NewTicker(gc.interval)\n145:     defer ticker.Stop()\n146: \n147:     klog.Info(\"GarbageCollector started\")\n148: \n149:     for {\n150:         select {\n151:         case <-gc.ctx.Done():\n152:             klog.Info(\"GarbageCollector stopped\")\n153:             return\n154:         case <-ticker.C:\n155:             gc.tick()\n156:         }\n157:     }\n158: }\n159: ```\n160: \n161: ### 场景: 设置单次 tick 超时\n162: \n163: **GIVEN** 单次 tick 可能耗时较长\n164: **WHEN** 执行 tick 方法\n165: **THEN** 为单次 tick 设置超时上下文，防止阻塞\n166: \n167: ```go\n168: func (gc *GarbageCollector) tick() {\n169:     tickCtx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(gc.ctx, GCSingleTickTimeout)\n170:     defer cancel()\n171: \n172:     now := time.Now()\n173:     idleThreshold := now.Add(-DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout)\n174:     expiredThreshold := now\n175: \n176:     idleSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListInactiveSandboxes(tickCtx, idleThreshold, 16)\n177:     if err != nil {\n178:         klog.Errorf(\"Failed to list inactive sandboxes: %v\", err)\n179:     } else {\n180:         for _, sandbox := range idleSandboxes {\n181:             gc.deleteSandbox(tickCtx, sandbox, wmTypes.CleanupReasonIdleTimeout)\n182:         }\n183:     }\n184: \n185:     expiredSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListExpiredSandboxes(tickCtx, expiredThreshold, 16)\n186:     if err != nil {\n187:         klog.Errorf(\"Failed to list expired sandboxes: %v\", err)\n188:     } else {\n189:         for _, sandbox := range expiredSandboxes {\n190:             gc.deleteSandbox(tickCtx, sandbox, wmTypes.CleanupReasonExpired)\n191:         }\n192:     }\n193: }\n194: ```\n195: \n196: ## 空闲 Sandbox 清理\n197: \n198: ### 场景: 查询空闲 Sandbox\n199: \n200: **GIVEN** 当前时间为 `now`\n201: **WHEN** 查询空闲超时的 Sandbox\n202: **THEN** 计算空闲阈值并从 store 查询\n203: \n204: ```go\n205: now := time.Now()\n206: idleThreshold := now.Add(-DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout)\n207: \n208: idleSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListInactiveSandboxes(tickCtx, idleThreshold, 16)\n209: ```\n210: \n211: ### 场景: 清理空闲 Sandbox\n212: \n213: **GIVEN** 查询到空闲的 Sandbox 列表\n214: **WHEN** 遍历空闲 Sandbox 列表\n215: **THEN** 对每个空闲 Sandbox 调用删除方法，原因为 `CleanupReasonIdleTimeout`\n216: \n217: ```go\n218: for _, sandbox := range idleSandboxes {\n219:     gc.deleteSandbox(tickCtx, sandbox, wmTypes.CleanupReasonIdleTimeout)\n220: }\n221: ```\n222: \n223: ## 过期 Sandbox 清理\n224: \n225: ### 场景: 查询过期 Sandbox\n226: \n227: **GIVEN** 当前时间为 `now`\n228: **WHEN** 查询过期的 Sandbox\n229: **THEN** 使用当前时间作为阈值从 store 查询\n230: \n231: ```go\n232: now := time.Now()\n233: expiredThreshold := now\n234: \n235: expiredSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListExpiredSandboxes(tickCtx, expiredThreshold, 16)\n236: ```\n237: \n238: ### 场景: 清理过期 Sandbox\n239: \n240: **GIVEN** 查询到过期的 Sandbox 列表\n241: **WHEN** 遍历过期 Sandbox 列表\n242: **THEN** 对每个过期 Sandbox 调用删除方法，原因为 `CleanupReasonExpired`\n243: \n244: ```go\n245: for _, sandbox := range expiredSandboxes {\n246:     gc.deleteSandbox(tickCtx, sandbox, wmTypes.CleanupReasonExpired)\n247: }\n248: ```\n249: \n250: ## Sandbox 删除\n251: \n252: ### 场景: 选择正确的 GVR\n253: \n254: **GIVEN** Sandbox 信息包含 Kind 字段\n255: **WHEN** 删除 Sandbox\n256: **THEN** 根据 Kind 选择正确的 GVR（Sandbox 或 SandboxClaim）\n257: \n258: ```go\n259: gvr := SandboxGVR\n260: if sandbox.Kind == \"SandboxClaim\" {\n261:     gvr = SandboxClaimGVR\n262: }\n263: ```\n264: \n265: ### 场景: 设置删除操作超时\n266: \n267: **GIVEN** 需要删除 Sandbox 资源\n268: **WHEN** 调用 Kubernetes API 删除\n269: **THEN** 为删除操作设置独立的超时上下文\n270: \n271: ```go\n272: deleteCtx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(ctx, DeleteTimeout)\n273: defer cancel()\n274: ```\n275: \n276: ### 场景: 删除 Sandbox 资源\n277: \n278: **GIVEN** 已确定正确的 GVR 和 namespace\n279: **WHEN** 调用 Kubernetes API 删除\n280: **THEN** 使用 dynamic client 删除资源\n281: \n282: ```go\n283: err := gc.dynamicClient.Resource(gvr).\n284:     Namespace(sandbox.SandboxNamespace).\n285:     Delete(deleteCtx, sandbox.SandboxID, metav1.DeleteOptions{})\n286: ```\n287: \n288: ### 场景: 处理删除成功\n289: \n290: **GIVEN** Kubernetes API 删除成功或资源不存在\n291: **WHEN** 删除操作完成\n292: **THEN** 从 store 中删除记录，标记审计为成功\n293: \n294: ```go\n295: if err := gc.storeClient.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sandbox.SessionID); err != nil {\n296:     klog.Warningf(\"Failed to delete sandbox %s from store: %v\", sandbox.SessionID, err)\n297: }\n298: auditEntry.Success = true\n299: klog.Infof(\"Deleted sandbox %s/%s (reason: %s)\", sandbox.SandboxNamespace, sandbox.SandboxID, reason)\n300: ```\n301: \n302: ### 场景: 处理删除失败\n303: \n304: **GIVEN** Kubernetes API 删除失败且不是 NotFound 错误\n305: **WHEN** 删除操作失败\n306: **THEN** 记录错误信息到审计，标记审计为失败\n307: \n308: ```go\n309: if err != nil && !apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n310:     auditEntry.ErrorMessage = err.Error()\n311:     auditEntry.Success = false\n312:     klog.Errorf(\"Failed to delete sandbox %s/%s: %v\", sandbox.SandboxNamespace, sandbox.SandboxID, err)\n313: }\n314: ```\n315: \n316: ## 审计日志\n317: \n318: ### 场景: 创建审计条目\n319: \n320: **GIVEN** 准备删除 Sandbox\n321: **WHEN** 创建审计日志条目\n322: **THEN** 记录所有关键信息\n323: \n324: ```go\n325: auditEntry := &wmTypes.CleanupAuditEntry{\n326:     SessionID: sandbox.SessionID,\n327:     SandboxID: sandbox.SandboxID,\n328:     Namespace: sandbox.SandboxNamespace,\n329:     Reason:    reason,\n330:     DeletedAt: time.Now(),\n331: }\n332: ```\n333: \n334: ### 场景: 记录审计日志\n335: \n336: **GIVEN** 删除操作完成\n337: **WHEN** 记录审计日志\n338: **THEN** 输出结构化的审计信息\n339: \n340: ```go\n341: func (gc *GarbageCollector) recordAudit(entry *wmTypes.CleanupAuditEntry) {\n342:     klog.Infof(\"Cleanup audit: sessionId=%s sandboxId=%s namespace=%s reason=%s success=%v deletedAt=%s\",\n343:         entry.SessionID, entry.SandboxID, entry.Namespace, entry.Reason, entry.Success, entry.DeletedAt.Format(time.RFC3339))\n344:     if entry.ErrorMessage != \"\" {\n345:         klog.Infof(\"Cleanup audit error: %s\", entry.ErrorMessage)\n346:     }\n347: }\n348: ```\n349: \n350: ## 错误处理\n351: \n352: ### 场景: 处理查询空闲 Sandbox 错误\n353: \n354: **GIVEN** 查询空闲 Sandbox 时发生错误\n355: **WHEN** 捕获错误\n356: **THEN** 记录错误日志，继续执行过期 Sandbox 查询\n357: \n358: ```go\n359: idleSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListInactiveSandboxes(tickCtx, idleThreshold, 16)\n360: if err != nil {\n361:     klog.Errorf(\"Failed to list inactive sandboxes: %v\", err)\n362: }\n363: ```\n364: \n365: ### 场景: 处理查询过期 Sandbox 错误\n366: \n367: **GIVEN** 查询过期 Sandbox 时发生错误\n368: **WHEN** 捕获错误\n369: **THEN** 记录错误日志\n370: \n371: ```go\n372: expiredSandboxes, err := gc.storeClient.ListExpiredSandboxes(tickCtx, expiredThreshold, 16)\n373: if err != nil {\n374:     klog.Errorf(\"Failed to list expired sandboxes: %v\", err)\n375: }\n376: ```\n377: \n378: ### 场景: 处理 Store 删除失败\n379: \n380: **GIVEN** Kubernetes 删除成功但 Store 删除失败\n381: **WHEN** Store 删除失败\n382: **THEN** 记录警告日志，不影响整体流程\n383: \n384: ```go\n385: if err := gc.storeClient.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sandbox.SessionID); err != nil {\n386:     klog.Warningf(\"Failed to delete sandbox %s from store: %v\", sandbox.SessionID, err)\n387: }\n388: ```\n389: \n390: ## 配置常量\n391: \n392: ### 场景: 定义 GC 间隔\n393: \n394: **GIVEN** 需要配置 GC 检查频率\n395: **WHEN** 定义 GC 间隔常量\n396: **THEN** 在 `defaults.go` 中设置合理的默认值\n397: \n398: ```go\n399: const (\n400:     GCInterval = 15 * time.Second\n401: )\n402: ```\n403: \n404: ### 场景: 定义空闲超时\n405: \n406: **GIVEN** 需要配置 Sandbox 空闲超时时间\n407: **WHEN** 定义空闲超时常量\n408: **THEN** 在 `defaults.go` 中设置默认值\n409: \n410: ```go\n411: const (\n412:     DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n413: )\n414: ```\n415: \n416: ### 场景: 定义超时配置\n417: \n418: **GIVEN** 需要配置各操作的超时时间\n419: **WHEN** 定义超时常量\n420: **THEN** 在 `defaults.go` 中设置合理的超时值\n421: \n422: ```go\n423: const (\n424:     GCSingleTickTimeout = 2 * time.Minute\n425:     DeleteTimeout       = 30 * time.Second\n426: )\n427: ```\n428: \n429: ## 测试场景\n430: \n431: ### 场景: 测试空闲 Sandbox 清理\n432: \n433: **GIVEN** 使用 fake store 和 fake dynamic client\n434: **WHEN** 测试 tick 方法清理空闲 Sandbox\n435: **THEN** 验证调用了正确的 store 方法和删除操作\n436: \n437: ```go\n438: func TestGarbageCollector_Tick_IdleSandboxes(t *testing.T) {\n439:     mockStore := &mockStoreForGC{}\n440:     idleSandboxes := []*types.SandboxInfo{\n441:         {\n442:             SessionID:        \"idle-session-1\",\n443:             SandboxID:        \"idle-sandbox-1\",\n444:             SandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n445:             Kind:             \"Sandbox\",\n446:         },\n447:     }\n448:     mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return(idleSandboxes, nil)\n449:     mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"idle-session-1\").Return(nil)\n450:     mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, nil)\n451: \n452:     scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n453:     fakeDynamicClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n454: \n455:     gc := NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, mockStore, GCInterval)\n456: \n457:     gc.tick()\n458: \n459:     mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16)\n460:     mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"idle-session-1\")\n461: }\n462: ```\n463: \n464: ### 场景: 测试过期 Sandbox 清理\n465: \n466: **GIVEN** 使用 fake store 和 fake dynamic client\n467: **WHEN** 测试 tick 方法清理过期 Sandbox\n468: **THEN** 验证调用了正确的 store 方法和删除操作\n469: \n470: ```go\n471: func TestGarbageCollector_Tick_ExpiredSandboxes(t *testing.T) {\n472:     mockStore := &mockStoreForGC{}\n473:     expiredSandboxes := []*types.SandboxInfo{\n474:         {\n475:             SessionID:        \"expired-session-1\",\n476:             SandboxID:        \"expired-sandbox-1\",\n477:             SandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n478:             Kind:             \"Sandbox\",\n479:         },\n480:     }\n481:     mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return(expiredSandboxes, nil)\n482:     mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"expired-session-1\").Return(nil)\n483:     mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, nil)\n484: \n485:     scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n486:     fakeDynamicClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n487: \n488:     gc := NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, mockStore, GCInterval)\n489: \n490:     gc.tick()\n491: \n492:     mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16)\n493:     mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"expired-session-1\")\n494: }\n495: ```\n496: \n497: ### 场景: 测试 Kubernetes NotFound 处理\n498: \n499: **GIVEN** Sandbox 在 Kubernetes 中已不存在\n500: **WHEN** GC 尝试删除该 Sandbox\n501: **THEN** 仍然从 store 中删除记录，不报错\n502: \n503: ```go\n504: func TestGarbageCollector_Tick_KubernetesNotFound(t *testing.T) {\n505:     mockStore := &mockStoreForGC{}\n506:     sandboxInfo := &types.SandboxInfo{\n507:         SessionID:        \"missing-session\",\n508:         SandboxID:        \"missing-sandbox\",\n509:         SandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n510:         Kind:             \"Sandbox\",\n511:     }\n512:     mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{sandboxInfo}, nil)\n513:     mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"missing-session\").Return(nil)\n514:     mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, nil)\n515: \n516:     scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n517:     fakeDynamicClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n518: \n519:     gc := NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, mockStore, GCInterval)\n520: \n521:     gc.tick()\n522: \n523:     mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"missing-session\")\n524: }\n525: ```\n526: \n527: ### 场景: 测试 GC 启动停止\n528: \n529: **GIVEN** 垃圾回收器实例已创建\n530: **WHEN** 启动 GC 并等待几次 tick 后停止\n531: **THEN** GC 能正常启动和停止，无 panic\n532: \n533: ```go\n534: func TestGarbageCollector_StartStop(t *testing.T) {\n535:     mockStore := &mockStoreForGC{}\n536:     mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, nil)\n537:     mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, nil)\n538: \n539:     scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n540:     fakeDynamicClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n541: \n542:     gc := NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, mockStore, 100*time.Millisecond)\n543: \n544:     gc.Start()\n545: \n546:     time.Sleep(250 * time.Millisecond)\n547: \n548:     gc.Stop()\n549: \n550:     time.Sleep(50 * time.Millisecond)\n551:     assert.True(t, true, \"GC stopped without panic\")\n552: }\n553: ```\n554: \n555: ### 场景: 测试查询错误处理\n556: \n557: **GIVEN** Store 返回查询错误\n558: **WHEN** GC 执行 tick\n559: **THEN** 记录错误日志并继续执行\n560: \n561: ```go\n562: func TestGarbageCollector_Tick_ListInactiveError(t *testing.T) {\n563:     mockStore := &mockStoreForGC{}\n564:     mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, assert.AnError)\n565:     mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return([]*types.SandboxInfo{}, nil)\n566: \n567:     scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n568:     fakeDynamicClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n569: \n570:     gc := NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, mockStore, GCInterval)\n571: \n572:     gc.tick()\n573: \n574:     mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16)\n575:     mockStore.AssertCalled(t, \"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16)\n576: }\n577: ```\n578: \n579: ### 场景: 测试同时清理空闲和过期 Sandbox\n580: \n581: **GIVEN** 同时存在空闲和过期的 Sandbox\n582: **WHEN** GC 执行 tick\n583: **THEN** 清理所有符合条件的 Sandbox\n584: \n585: ```go\n586: func TestGarbageCollector_Tick_BothLists(t *testing.T) {\n587:     mockStore := &mockStoreForGC{}\n588:     idleSandboxes := []*types.SandboxInfo{\n589:         {\n590:             SessionID:        \"idle-session-1\",\n591:             SandboxID:        \"idle-sandbox-1\",\n592:             SandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n593:             Kind:             \"Sandbox\",\n594:         },\n595:     }\n596:     expiredSandboxes := []*types.SandboxInfo{\n597:         {\n598:             SessionID:        \"expired-session-1\",\n599:             SandboxID:        \"expired-sandbox-1\",\n600:             SandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n601:             Kind:             \"Sandbox\",\n602:         },\n603:     }\n604:     mockStore.On(\"ListInactiveSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return(idleSandboxes, nil)\n605:     mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"idle-session-1\").Return(nil)\n606:     mockStore.On(\"ListExpiredSandboxes\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, 16).Return(expiredSandboxes, nil)\n607:     mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"expired-session-1\").Return(nil)\n608: \n609:     scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n610:     fakeDynamicClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n611: \n612:     gc := NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, mockStore, GCInterval)\n613: \n614:     gc.tick()\n615: \n616:     mockStore.AssertNumberOfCalls(t, \"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", 2)\n617: }\n618: ```\n619: \n620: ## 最终验证\n621: \n622: ### 场景: 验证 GC 完整功能\n623: \n624: **GIVEN** 所有 GC 组件已实现\n625: **WHEN** 运行完整测试套件\n626: **THEN** 所有单元测试通过，GC 能够正确清理空闲和过期的 Sandbox\n627: \n628: ### 场景: 验证 GC 性能\n629: \n630: **GIVEN** GC 已部署到生产环境\n631: **WHEN** 存在大量 Sandbox 需要清理\n632: **THEN** GC 能够稳定运行，单次 tick 在超时时间内完成\n633: \n634: ### 场景: 验证审计日志完整性\n635: \n636: **GIVEN** GC 正在运行\n637: **WHEN** 清理 Sandbox\n638: **THEN** 所有清理操作都有完整的审计日志记录\n639: \n640: ## 文件组织\n641: \n642: ### 场景: 文件结构清晰分离\n643: \n644: **GIVEN** pkg/workloadmanager 模块需要组织 GC 代码\n645: **WHEN** 创建文件结构\n646: **THEN** 按职责分离文件：\n647: \n648: ```\n649: pkg/workloadmanager/\n650: ├── garbage_collector.go       # GarbageCollector 核心实现\n651: ├── garbage_collector_test.go  # 单元测试\n652: ├── types/\n653: │   └── sandbox_types.go       # Sandbox 相关类型定义\n654: └── defaults.go                # 配置常量\n655: ```\n\n(End of file - total 655 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n\n**Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** S\n\n## 垃圾回收核心结构\n\n### 场景: 定义 GarbageCollector 结构体\n\n**GIVEN** 需要定时清理空闲和过期的 Sandbox 资源\n**WHEN** 定义垃圾回收器核心结构体\n**THEN** 创建 `garbage_collector.go` 文件，定义 `GarbageCollector` 结构体\n\n```go\ntype GarbageCollector struct {\n    dynamicClient dynamic.Interface\n    storeClient   store.Store\n    interval      time.Duration\n    ctx           context.Context","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775849862277,"end":1775849862293}}}}
