   - 缓存命中率测试\n   - 延迟测试\n   - 并发测试\n\n### Phase 7: 文档和配置 (Day 8)\n\n1. 更新配置文档\n2. 更新 API 文档\n3. 添加使用示例\n4. 更新部署文档\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n1. **SessionManager 测试**\n   - `GetSandboxBySession` 缓存命中\n   - `GetSandboxBySession` 缓存未命中\n   - `CreateSession` 成功场景\n   - `CreateSession` WorkloadManager 错误\n   - `CreateSession` 验证错误\n\n2. **验证函数测试**\n   - `validateKind` 有效/无效输入\n   - `isValidNamespace` 有效/无效输入\n   - `isValidResourceName` 有效/无效输入\n\n3. **错误处理测试**\n   - 错误类型识别\n   - 错误码映射\n   - 错误信息格式\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n1. **Redis 集成测试**\n   - 使用 test Redis 实例\n","exit":0,"description":"Read more AR-010 from proposal.md","truncated":false},"title":"Read more AR-010 from proposal.md","time":{"start":1775849884395,"end":1775849884405}}}}
