{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775849981289,"sessionID":"ses_28719b16dffecOLQtjnU5U7KHJ","part":{"id":"prt_d78e8448f001Oj6yp15iTpi51t","messageID":"msg_d78e6f0ce001iskXDKYDBNv1gQ","sessionID":"ses_28719b16dffecOLQtjnU5U7KHJ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-f2a757f2bb7942b4ae882f2d98cca4d0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-010 — Router 会话管理\n\n**Module:** `pkg/router`\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** M\n\n## SessionManager 接口定义\n\n### 场景: 定义 SessionManager 接口\n\n**GIVEN** 需要管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的会话生命周期\n**WHEN** 定义 SessionManager 接口\n**THEN** 在 `session_manager.go` 中定义接口方法\n\n```go\ntype SessionManager interface {\n    GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n    CreateSession(ctx context.Context, name string, namespace string, kind string) (string, *types.SandboxInfo, error)\n}\n```\n\n## SessionManager 初始化\n\n### 场景: 创建 SessionManager 实例\n\n**GIVEN** 有可用的 store client 和 workload manager 地址\n**WHEN** 调用 NewSessionManager\n**THEN** 返回初始化好的 SessionManager 实例\n\n```go\nfunc NewSessionManager(storeClient store.Store, workloadMgrAddr string) (SessionManager, error)\n```\n\n### 场景: 验证必需参数\n\n**GIVEN** 创建 SessionManager\n**WHEN** store client 为 nil 或 workload manager 地址为空\n**THEN** 返回错误\n\n```go\nif storeClient == nil {\n    return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"store client is required\")\n}\n\nif workloadMgrAddr == \"\" {\n    return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"workload manager address is required\")\n}\n```\n\n## 会话创建\n\n### 场景: 创建新的 AgentRuntime 会话\n\n**GIVEN** 用户请求调用 AgentRuntime\n**WHEN** 调用 CreateSession 且 kind 为 AgentRuntimeKind\n**THEN** 向 WorkloadManager 创建会话并返回会话 ID 和沙箱信息\n\n```go\nsessionID, sandboxInfo, err := sessionManager.CreateSession(ctx, \"my-agent\", \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n```\n\n### 场景: 创建新的 CodeInterpreter 会话\n\n**GIVEN** 用户请求调用 CodeInterpreter\n**WHEN** 调用 CreateSession 且 kind 为 CodeInterpreterKind\n**THEN** 向 WorkloadManager 创建会话并返回会话 ID 和沙箱信息\n\n```go\nsessionID, sandboxInfo, err := sessionManager.CreateSession(ctx, \"my-interpreter\", \"default\", types.CodeInterpreterKind)\n```\n\n### 场景: 验证 Kind 类型\n\n**GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession\n**WHEN** kind 不是 AgentRuntimeKind 或 CodeInterpreterKind\n**THEN** 返回验证错误\n\n```go\nfunc validateKind(kind string) error {\n    if kind != types.AgentRuntimeKind && kind != types.CodeInterpreterKind {\n        return fmt.Errorf(\"invalid kind: %s, must be %s or %s\", kind, types.AgentRuntimeKind, types.CodeInterpreterKind)\n    }\n    return nil\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 验证命名空间格式\n\n**GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession\n**WHEN** namespace 格式无效\n**THEN** 返回 ValidationError\n\n```go\nfunc isValidNamespace(namespace string) bool {\n    if namespace == \"\" {\n        return false\n    }\n    if len(namespace) > 63 {\n        return false\n    }\n    return namespaceRegex.MatchString(namespace)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 验证资源名称格式\n\n**GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession\n**WHEN** name 格式无效\n**THEN** 返回 ValidationError\n\n```go\nfunc isValidResourceName(name string) bool {\n    if name == \"\" {\n        return false\n    }\n    if len(name) > 253 {\n        return false\n    }\n    return resourceNameRegex.MatchString(name)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 构造 WorkloadManager 请求\n\n**GIVEN** 创建会话的参数已验证\n**WHEN** 构造 HTTP 请求到 WorkloadManager\n**THEN** 根据 kind 选择正确的 endpoint\n\n```go\nif kind == types.AgentRuntimeKind {\n    endpoint = fmt.Sprintf(\"%s/v1/agent-runtime\", m.workloadMgrAddr)\n} else {\n    endpoint = fmt.Sprintf(\"%s/v1/code-interpreter\", m.workloadMgrAddr)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 处理 WorkloadManager 创建成功\n\n**GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回 200 OK\n**WHEN** 解析响应\n**THEN** 提取 sessionID 并查询完整沙箱信息\n\n```go\nvar createResp WorkloadManagerCreateResponse\nif err := json.Unmarshal(body, &createResp); err != nil {\n    return \"\", nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to unmarshal create response: %w\", err)\n}\n\nsessionID := createResp.SessionID\n```\n\n### 场景: 处理 WorkloadManager 创建失败\n\n**GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回非 200 状态码\n**WHEN** 创建会话失败\n**THEN** 返回 WorkloadManagerError\n\n```go\nif resp.StatusCode != http.StatusOK {\n    return \"\", nil, &WorkloadManagerError{\n        Message: string(body),\n        Code:    resp.StatusCode,\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 会话查询\n\n### 场景: 从缓存获取会话\n\n**GIVEN** 会话已存在于 Redis 缓存\n**WHEN** 调用 GetSandboxBySession\n**THEN** 从 store 返回沙箱信息，记录缓存命中\n\n```go\nfunc (m *manager) GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error) {\n    sandboxInfo, err := m.storeClient.GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)\n    if err == nil {\n        klog.V(4).Infof(\"Cache hit for session: %s\", sessionID)\n        return sandboxInfo, nil\n    }\n    // ...\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 缓存未命中时查询 WorkloadManager\n\n**GIVEN** 会话不在 Redis 缓存中\n**WHEN** 调用 GetSandboxBySession\n**THEN** 向 WorkloadManager 查询会话信息\n\n```go\nif err != nil {\n    if err == store.ErrNotFound {\n        klog.V(4).Infof(\"Cache miss for session: %s, querying workload manager\", sessionID)\n        return m.getSandboxFromWorkloadManager(ctx, sessionID)\n    }\n    // ...\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: WorkloadManager 查询成功并缓存\n\n**GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回会话信息\n**WHEN** 查询成功\n**THEN** 将沙箱信息存入 Redis 缓存\n\n```go\nsandboxInfo := SandboxInfoFromWorkloadManager(&getSessionResp, sessionID)\n\nif err := m.storeClient.StoreSandbox(ctx, sessionID, sandboxInfo); err != nil {\n    klog.Warningf(\"Failed to cache sandbox info: %v\", err)\n}\n\nreturn sandboxInfo, nil\n```\n\n### 场景: WorkloadManager 返回 404\n\n**GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回 404 Not Found\n**WHEN** 查询会话\n**THEN** 返回 SandboxNotFoundError\n\n```go\nif resp.StatusCode == http.StatusNotFound {\n    return nil, &SandboxNotFoundError{SessionID: sessionID}\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: WorkloadManager 返回其他错误\n\n**GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回非 200 和非 404 状态码\n**WHEN** 查询会话失败\n**THEN** 返回 WorkloadManagerError\n\n```go\nif resp.StatusCode != http.StatusOK {\n    return nil, &WorkloadManagerError{\n        Message: string(body),\n        Code:    resp.StatusCode,\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 类型转换\n\n### 场景: 转换 WorkloadManager 响应为 SandboxInfo\n\n**GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回会话响应\n**WHEN** 转换为内部类型\n**THEN** 正确映射所有字段\n\n```go\nfunc SandboxInfoFromWorkloadManager(resp *WorkloadManagerGetSessionResponse, sessionID string) *types.SandboxInfo {\n    createdAt, _ := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, resp.CreatedAt)\n    expiresAt, _ := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, resp.ExpiresAt)\n    lastActivity, _ := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, resp.LastActivity)\n\n    return &types.SandboxInfo{\n        Kind:             resp.Kind,\n        SandboxID:        resp.SandboxID,\n        SandboxName:      resp.SandboxName,\n        SandboxNamespace: resp.Namespace,\n        Name:             resp.Name,\n        EntryPoints:      resp.EntryPoints,\n        SessionID:        sessionID,\n        CreatedAt:        createdAt,\n        ExpiresAt:        expiresAt,\n        Status:           \"Ready\",\n        PodIP:            resp.PodIP,\n        Namespace:        resp.Namespace,\n        LastActivityAt:   lastActivity,\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 错误处理\n\n### 场景: 处理存储错误\n\n**GIVEN** Redis 操作失败\n**WHEN** 发生存储错误\n**THEN** 记录警告日志，不阻断流程\n\n```go\nif err := m.storeClient.StoreSandbox(ctx, sessionID, sandboxInfo); err != nil {\n    klog.Warningf(\"Failed to cache sandbox info: %v\", err)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 处理 HTTP 超时\n\n**GIVEN** WorkloadManager 响应超时\n**WHEN** HTTP 调用超时\n**THEN** 返回服务不可用错误\n\n```go\nhttpClient: &http.Client{Timeout: 30 * time.Second}\n```\n\n### 场景: 处理 JSON 解析错误\n\n**GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回无效 JSON\n**WHEN** 解析响应失败\n**THEN** 返回格式化错误\n\n```go\nif err := json.Unmarshal(body, &createResp); err != nil {\n    return \"\", nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to unmarshal create response: %w\", err)\n}\n```\n\n## 测试场景\n\n### 场景: 测试缓存命中\n\n**GIVEN** 会话存在于 Redis\n**WHEN** 调用 GetSandboxBySession\n**THEN** 直接从 Redis 返回，不调用 WorkloadManager\n\n```go\nfunc TestSessionManager_GetSandboxBySession_CacheHit(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    expectedSandbox := &types.SandboxInfo{\n        SessionID: \"test-session\",\n        SandboxID: \"test-sandbox\",\n    }\n    mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\").Return(expectedSandbox, nil)\n\n    sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n\n    result, err := sm.GetSandboxBySession(context.Background(), \"test-session\", \"default\", \"test-agent\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.Equal(t, expectedSandbox, result)\n    mockStore.AssertExpectations(t)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试缓存未命中并回源\n\n**GIVEN** 会话不存在于 Redis\n**WHEN** 调用 GetSandboxBySession\n**THEN** 调用 WorkloadManager 并缓存结果\n\n```go\nfunc TestSessionManager_GetSandboxBySession_CacheMiss(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n    expectedSandbox := &types.SandboxInfo{\n        SessionID: \"test-session\",\n        SandboxID: \"test-sandbox\",\n    }\n\n    mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\").Return(nil, store.ErrNotFound)\n    mockStore.On(\"StoreSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\", mock.Anything).Return(nil)\n\n    sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n    sm.httpClient = mockHTTPClient\n\n    result, err := sm.GetSandboxBySession(context.Background(), \"test-session\", \"default\", \"test-agent\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.Equal(t, expectedSandbox.SandboxID, result.SandboxID)\n    mockStore.AssertExpectations(t)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试创建会话成功\n\n**GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession 且所有参数有效\n**WHEN** WorkloadManager 成功创建会话\n**THEN** 返回 sessionID 和沙箱信息\n\n```go\nfunc TestSessionManager_CreateSession_Success(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n\n    createResponse := &WorkloadManagerCreateResponse{\n        SessionID:   \"new-session-id\",\n        SandboxID:   \"new-sandbox-id\",\n        SandboxName: \"test-agent\",\n        EntryPoints: []types.SandboxEntryPoint{{Path: \"/\", Port: 8080}},\n    }\n\n    getSessionResponse := &WorkloadManagerGetSessionResponse{\n        SessionID:    \"new-session-id\",\n        SandboxID:    \"new-sandbox-id\",\n        SandboxName:  \"test-agent\",\n        Kind:         types.AgentRuntimeKind,\n        Namespace:    \"default\",\n        Name:         \"test-agent\",\n        EntryPoints:  []types.SandboxEntryPoint{{Path: \"/\", Port: 8080}},\n        LastActivity: time.Now().Format(time.RFC3339),\n        CreatedAt:    time.Now().Format(time.RFC3339),\n        ExpiresAt:    time.Now().Add(8 * time.Hour).Format(time.RFC3339),\n    }\n\n    mockStore.On(\"StoreSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"new-session-id\", mock.Anything).Return(nil)\n    mockHTTPClient.SetupCreateResponse(200, createResponse)\n    mockHTTPClient.SetupGetSessionResponse(200, getSessionResponse)\n\n    sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n    sm.httpClient = mockHTTPClient\n\n    sessionID, sandboxInfo, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), \"test-agent\", \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"new-session-id\", sessionID)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"new-sandbox-id\", sandboxInfo.SandboxID)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试无效 Kind\n\n**GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession 且 kind 无效\n**WHEN** kind 不是 AgentRuntimeKind 或 CodeInterpreterKind\n**THEN** 返回验证错误\n\n```go\nfunc TestSessionManager_CreateSession_InvalidKind(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n\n    _, _, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), \"test-agent\", \"default\", \"InvalidKind\")\n\n    assert.Error(t, err)\n    assert.Contains(t, err.Error(), \"invalid kind\")\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试无效命名空间\n\n**GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession 且 namespace 格式无效\n**WHEN** namespace 包含大写字母\n**THEN** 返回 ValidationError\n\n```go\nfunc TestSessionManager_CreateSession_InvalidNamespace(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n\n    _, _, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), \"test-agent\", \"InvalidNamespace\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n\n    assert.Error(t, err)\n    _, ok := err.(*ValidationError)\n    assert.True(t, ok)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"namespace\", err.(*ValidationError).Field)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试无效资源名称\n\n**GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession 且 name 格式无效\n**WHEN** name 超过长度限制\n**THEN** 返回 ValidationError\n\n```go\nfunc TestSessionManager_CreateSession_InvalidName(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n\n    longName := strings.Repeat(\"a\", 254)\n    _, _, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), longName, \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n\n    assert.Error(t, err)\n    _, ok := err.(*ValidationError)\n    assert.True(t, ok)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"name\", err.(*ValidationError).Field)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试 WorkloadManager 创建失败\n\n**GIVEN** 调用 CreateSession\n**WHEN** WorkloadManager 返回 500 错误\n**THEN** 返回 WorkloadManagerError\n\n```go\nfunc TestSessionManager_CreateSession_WorkloadManagerError(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n\n    mockHTTPClient.SetupCreateResponse(500, nil)\n\n    sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n    sm.httpClient = mockHTTPClient\n\n    _, _, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), \"test-agent\", \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n\n    assert.Error(t, err)\n    _, ok := err.(*WorkloadManagerError)\n    assert.True(t, ok)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试会话未找到\n\n**GIVEN** 查询不存在的会话\n**WHEN** WorkloadManager 返回 404\n**THEN** 返回 SandboxNotFoundError\n\n```go\nfunc TestSessionManager_GetSandboxBySession_NotFound(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n\n    mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"nonexistent-session\").Return(nil, store.ErrNotFound)\n    mockHTTPClient.SetupGetSessionResponse(404, nil)\n\n    sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n    sm.httpClient = mockHTTPClient\n\n    _, err := sm.GetSandboxBySession(context.Background(), \"nonexistent-session\", \"default\", \"test-agent\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n\n    assert.Error(t, err)\n    _, ok := err.(*SandboxNotFoundError)\n    assert.True(t, ok)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试存储失败降级\n\n**GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回会话信息但 Redis 失败\n**WHEN** 缓存操作失败\n**THEN** 仍返回会话信息，记录警告\n\n```go\nfunc TestSessionManager_GetSandboxBySession_StoreFailure(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n\n    getSessionResponse := &WorkloadManagerGetSessionResponse{\n        SessionID:    \"test-session\",\n        SandboxID:    \"test-sandbox\",\n        SandboxName:  \"test-agent\",\n        Kind:         types.AgentRuntimeKind,\n        Namespace:    \"default\",\n        Name:         \"test-agent\",\n        EntryPoints:  []types.SandboxEntryPoint{{Path: \"/\", Port: 8080}},\n        LastActivity: time.Now().Format(time.RFC3339),\n        CreatedAt:    time.Now().Format(time.RFC3339),\n        ExpiresAt:    time.Now().Add(8 * time.Hour).Format(time.RFC3339),\n    }\n\n    mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\").Return(nil, store.ErrNotFound)\n    mockStore.On(\"StoreSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\", mock.Anything).Return(assert.AnError)\n    mockHTTPClient.SetupGetSessionResponse(200, getSessionResponse)\n\n    sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n    sm.httpClient = mockHTTPClient\n\n    result, err := sm.GetSandboxBySession(context.Background(), \"test-session\", \"default\", \"test-agent\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"test-sandbox\", result.SandboxID)\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 测试 HTTP 超时\n\n**GIVEN** WorkloadManager 响应缓慢\n**WHEN** HTTP 调用超时\n**THEN** 返回错误\n\n```go\nfunc TestSessionManager_CreateSession_HTTPTimeout(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n\n    mockHTTPClient.SetupTimeout()\n\n    sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n    sm.httpClient = mockHTTPClient\n\n    _, _, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), \"test-agent\", \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n\n    assert.Error(t, err)\n    assert.Contains(t, err.Error(), \"timeout\")\n}\n```\n\n## 配置\n\n### 场景: 配置 WorkloadManager 地址\n\n**GIVEN** 需要连接到 WorkloadManager\n**WHEN** 初始化 SessionManager\n**THEN** 通过构造函数传入 WorkloadManager 地址\n\n```go\nworkloadMgrAddr := \"http://workload-manager:8080\"\nsm, err := NewSessionManager(storeClient, workloadMgrAddr)\n```\n\n### 场景: 配置 HTTP 超时\n\n**GIVEN** 需要控制 HTTP 超时时间\n**WHEN** 创建 HTTP 客户端\n**THEN** 设置合理的超时值\n\n```go\nhttpClient: &http.Client{Timeout: 30 * time.Second}\n```\n\n## 集成测试\n\n### 场景: 端到端会话创建和查询\n\n**GIVEN** 启动完整的 Router 服务\n**WHEN** 发送创建会话请求\n**THEN** 会话成功创建并可查询\n\n```go\nfunc TestE2E_SessionCreation(t *testing.T) {\n    // 1. 启动 WorkloadManager mock\n    // 2. 启动 Redis\n    // 3. 创建 SessionManager\n    // 4. 调用 CreateSession\n    // 5. 验证返回\n    // 6. 使用 sessionID 调用 GetSandboxBySession\n    // 7. 验证缓存命中\n}\n```\n\n### 场景: 并发会话创建\n\n**GIVEN** 多个并发请求创建会话\n**WHEN** 同时调用 CreateSession\n**THEN** 所有会话成功创建且 sessionID 唯一\n\n```go\nfunc TestSessionManager_CreateSession_Concurrent(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    mockHTTPClient := &mockHTTPClient{}\n\n    sessionIDs := make(map[string]bool)\n    var mu sync.Mutex\n\n    sm, _ := NewSessionManager(mockStore, \"http://test-wm\")\n\n    var wg sync.WaitGroup\n    for i := 0; i < 10; i++ {\n        wg.Add(1)\n        go func(n int) {\n            defer wg.Done()\n            sessionID, _, err := sm.CreateSession(context.Background(), fmt.Sprintf(\"agent-%d\", n), \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n            assert.NoError(t, err)\n\n            mu.Lock()\n            defer mu.Unlock()\n            assert.False(t, sessionIDs[sessionID], \"duplicate session ID: %s\", sessionID)\n            sessionIDs[sessionID] = true\n        }(i)\n    }\n\n    wg.Wait()\n    assert.Equal(t, 10, len(sessionIDs))\n}\n```\n\n## 验收标准\n\n### 场景: 验证会话创建成功率\n\n**GIVEN** 大量创建会话请求\n**WHEN** 统计成功率\n**THEN** 成功率 > 99%\n\n### 场景: 验证缓存命中率\n\n**GIVEN** 多次查询同一会话\n**WHEN** 统计缓存命中\n**THEN** 缓存命中率 > 90%\n\n### 场景: 验证查询延迟\n\n**GIVEN** 缓存命中场景\n**WHEN** 测量查询延迟\n**THEN** P99 延迟 < 10ms\n\n### 场景: 验证零会话冲突\n\n**GIVEN** 大量并发会话创建\n**WHEN** 检查 sessionID\n**THEN** 无重复 sessionID\n\n## 文件组织\n\n### 场景: 文件结构清晰\n\n**GIVEN** pkg/router 模块组织代码\n**WHEN** 创建文件结构\n**THEN** 按职责分离文件：\n\n```\npkg/router/\n├── session_manager.go       # SessionManager 核心实现\n├── session_manager_test.go  # 单元测试\n├── handlers.go              # HTTP 处理器\n├── middleware.go            # 中间件\n├── jwt.go                   # JWT 管理\n├── proxy.go                 # 反向代理\n├── server.go                # HTTP 服务器\n├── config.go                # 配置\n├── types.go                 # 类型定义\n├── errors.go                # 错误定义\n├── utils.go                 # 工具函数\n└── doc.go                   # 包文档\n```","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/controller/reconciler/codeinterpreter.go\">\nERROR [63:7] undefined: statusConditionsEqual\nERROR [106:6] undefined: statusConditionsEqual\nERROR [173:2] declared and not used: logger\nERROR [242:5] undefined: podSpecsEqual\nERROR [267:29] undefined: convertEnvVars\nERROR [274:25] undefined: convertResources\nERROR [326:6] undefined: statusConditionsEqual\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/controller/reconciler/controller.go\">\nERROR [57:3] unknown field MetricsBindAddress in struct